      "text": "This can be an advantage, insofar as every position can be countered by a [[Negation]], every discussion of one context by the discussion of another; communication remains open, does not suffer from general consistency constraints, and can therefore function cafeteria-like on the market of the already sparse usability of sociological insights and skills: It can, because it brings much, bring some. Thereby, it is not necessary to pay attention to the fact that what one person gets competes conceptually with what another person could give."
